.SH COMMON FAILURES
.IP \(bu 2
Treating the raw Gradle updates plugin output as the only source of
truth.
.IP \(bu 2
Expecting \f[CR]task init\f[R] in a fresh starter workspace to avoid
downloading project\-local dependencies.
.IP \(bu 2
Forgetting to rerun the full task workflow after version changes.
.IP \(bu 2
Ignoring scan artifacts after a dependency update.
.SH GUIDANCE
.IP \(bu 2
Let the task workflow drive Gradle operations unless you have a specific
reason not to.
.IP \(bu 2
Prefer normalized report artifacts when triaging multiple update
candidates.
.IP \(bu 2
Keep the verification loop intact after dependency changes.
.IP \(bu 2
Treat \f[CR]task test\f[R] as the full bar and use focused
\f[CR]task test:*\f[R] helpers for suite\-level diagnostics.
